GPFA_array_out_circle_NumTrials_x_Time45_x_Neurons.RDS
'array': numeric [1:40, 1:45, 1:325] 

   - dim 1: window (j=1,...,38 IN; j=1,...,40 OUT)
   - dim 2: time (t=1,...,45)
   - dim 3: neuron (i=1,...,325)
each cell is the number of spikes for neuron i at time t, during window j.


